quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  13,29,"ЖЃeen gooЕ‹Й—iiЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖґЖґe, welo-welo woodaniiЙ“e e moЖґЖґude ruttorde."
  13,30,"Ko wano nii min nulir-maa e mofte - gooЕ‹Й—ii mofte goo yawtiino ado majje - fii yo a janngan Й“e nden nde min wahayini e maaЙ—a, kono heЙ“e yedda YurmeteeЙ—o on. maaku: "Ko KaЕ‹ko woni Joomi am. deweteeЙ—o alaa si wanaa KaЕ‹ko. Ko e makko mi fawii, ko ka makko kadi woni ruttorde am"."
  13,31,"Sinno janngeteende naЙ“irano pelle Й—e, maa leydi ndin seekiraa sabu mayre, maa nde wowliniraa maayЙ“e Й“en (harayno ko ndee Й—oo). Ko woni, ko Alla woodani fiyaaku on fow. E gooЕ‹Й—inЙ“e Й“en nganndaanii wonВґde, sinno Alla muuyuno, o fewnatna denndaangal yimЙ“e Й“en? Masiibo seeraani no heЙ“ira yedduЙ“e Й“een ko Й“e paggitii kon, maa [ngon masiibo] yana takko galle maЙ“Й“e nden haa fodoore Alla nden ara. Pellet Alla firtataa fodoore."
  13,32,"GoЕ‹Й—ii nulaaЙ“e njalkitanoo ma ado maaЙ—a. mi muГ±Г±anii Й“en yedduЙ“e, refti Mi nanngi Й“e. Ko honno lepte am Й—en ngonirnoo!"
  13,33,"E hara ko oon dariiЙ—o e kala woЕ‹kii ko ki faggitii kon [Й“uri hanndude e dewal?...] ЖЃe mbaЙ—anii Alla kafidii- Й—i. Maaku: "Innee-Й—i" Kaa on humpitay mo ko o ngnndaa ka leydi? Kaa ko ko [tun] e konngol? Ko woni, heeferЙ“e Й“een cuЙ—inanaa ma pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—een, Й“e sakkaa(pala) e laawol ngol. Kala mo Alla majjini, peewnoowo alanaa mo."
  13,34,"Hino woodani Й“e lepte ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet ko lepte laakara Й—en Й“uri sattude, alanaa Й“e daЙ—ndoowo (Й“e) e Alla."